label: contentLayerQuantity
comment: A number of content layers in this logistics packaging.
The number of content layers that are or may be packaged with this supply chain packaging, such as the number of layers of product on a pallet.

domainIncludes.comment: Any wrapping or containment, such as a box or a barrel, whether or not any goods are contained within.
Any material with which supply chain goods are packaged, such as a box or bubble wrap.
